@match send
@cond $who->pay_amount (5)
@setflag valdor_travel 1
@trigger 1
Thank you!

<starts to make some gestures>

@match send
@setflag valdor_travel 1
@trigger 1
Since you do not have enough money, we will sponsor you this time.

<starts to make some gestures>

@match hi
Welcome!

If you want to know more about Valdor Tourism, please ask Dabor in the front.

Travel to Valdor costs 5 silver, travel back is free.

If you want me to send you there now, just tell me so.

<he looks very exhausted>

@match *
If you want to know more about Valdor Tourism, please ask Dabor in the front.
endmsg
